{"lemma":"شاخِصَةٍ","slug":"شاخِصَةٍ","root":"ش.خ.ص","root_slug":"ش-خ-ص","root_link":"/words/roots/ش-خ-ص","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"شاخِصَةٍ","root":"شخص","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["adj","noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":6},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n21903"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B4%D8%A7%D8%AE%D9%90%D8%B5%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"active participle of شَخَصَ (šaḵaṣa)","tags":["active","form-of","participle"]},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"fixed"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"staring, gazing"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"projecting, standing out or upright"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"index, standard"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"gnomon (on a sundial)","tags":["historical"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Derived from the active participle of شَخَصَ (šaḵaṣa)."},"ipa":["/ʃaː.xisˤ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n21903","headword_ar":"شَاخِصٌ","root":"$xS","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[part. n. of the intrans. verb"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$axaSa","text_ar":"شَخَصَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baSarN $aAxiSN","text_ar":"بَصَرٌ شَاخِصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An eye fixedly open:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"raised:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sight stretched and raised:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see 1]: you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"samiEotu biquduwmika faqalobiY bayona janaAHaY~a","text_ar":"سَمِعْتُ بِقُدُومِكَ فَقَلْبِى بَيْنَ جَنَاحَىَّ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raAqiSN wabaSariY taHota HijaAjiY $aAxiSN","text_ar":"رَاقِصٌ وَبَصَرِى تَحْتَ حِجَاجِى شَاخِصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I have heard of thy coming, and my heart"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"throbbing between my two sides, and my eye beneath my bone of the eyebrow fixedly open,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]. (A, TA.) With the pl.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aboSaArN","text_ar":"اَبْصَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", you say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aAxiSapN","text_ar":"شَاخِصَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, Msb, TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$awaAxiSu","text_ar":"شَوَاخِصُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, TA,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uxuwSN","text_ar":"شُخُوصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uhuwdN","text_ar":"شُهُودٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"as pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aAhidN","text_ar":"شَاهِدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; if not an inf. n., as which it may be applied, in the place of an epithet, to a pl. subst.]. (Msb.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sahomN $aAxiSN","text_ar":"سَهْمٌ شَاخِصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An arrow passing beyond the butt,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"object of aim, going above it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rumiYa biAl$~aAxiSaAti","text_ar":"رُمِىَ بِالشَّاخِصَاتِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was shot at with arrows which passed beyond him, going above him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"perhaps doubly tropical, meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he was assailed with invectives which did not harm him"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aAxiSN","text_ar":"شَاخِصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies A man"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"prosecuting war"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"during three or more days together,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not on alternate days:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and of such it is said in a trad., that he may shorten prayer. (TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aAxiSN","text_ar":"شَاخِصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"as the act. part. n. of the trans. verb, [for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aAxiSN baSarahu","text_ar":"شَاخِصٌ بَصَرَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] (Msb,) (assumed tropical:)  [A man"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"raising his eye,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sight, and looking fixedly;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as does a dying man: or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stretching and raising his sight:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(see 1:) or] a man"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"opening his eyes and not moving his eyelids."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * Msb.)"}],"source_refs":["A","Msb","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}